column2: select * from optw.tamass.VARIABLES where UNIT = # and CONCEPT like #) select Commute = REPLACE (MIN (b.label) , #, #) , N = sum (v.VAL) , binmax from optw.tamass.VALS v join bins b on b.ID = v.VARID join optw.tamass.TRACTS t on t.ID = v.TRACTID where t.vintage = # and geom.STArea () < #e9 -- m^# -- excluding huge tracts and geom.STDistance (@center) < # / # * # -- meters group by VARID order by VARID asc
